data.value:
Beat the Dealer
1) Draw a hand value that is higher than the dealer’s hand value 2) The dealer draws a hand value that goes over 21 3) Draw a hand value of 21 on your first two cards, when the dealer does not
Scenarios to avoid
1) Your hand value exceeds 21 2) The dealer’s hand has a greater value than yours (and less than 21) at the end of the round
